{"tid":1218680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［反送中］［輿論戰］有冇人可以整一個大陸司法有問題嘅案件 list 出嚟","createTime":"2019-06-13T16:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T16:58:50.000Z","uid":48516,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8481b92facdf668f67558d02e8d0fce0a37656a0","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:29:37.000Z","msg":"聽到好多港豬都話唔犯法就無事，但好似有好多平民無端捲入官司，而又喺大陸得唔到公平嘅審訊。<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<br />\n谷開來案： 只有政府指定律師，審訊唔公開，案件詳細資料無公開<br />\n<br />\n豆腐渣工程：黃琦撰文揭發學校的豆腐渣工程，並協助死難者的父母提出申訴，其家人在6月14日接到通知「涉嫌非法持有國家機密」將其拘留。<br />\n<br />\n楊佳案：因騎一輛無牌照自行車，受到民警的詢問和盤查，後來獲釋。然而和許多同類情況一樣，楊遭毆打至生殖器損毁。楊多次上訪均未獲合理賠償，後來更不獲理睬<br />\n<br />\n瓮安事件：少女李樹芬於瓮安縣墜河身亡。李樹芬死亡原因有可疑之處，但當局不作立案，並強行要求將屍體埋葬，李樹芬家人作出阻止遭到毆打。<br />\n<br />\n新百倫：中國法院裁決一名註冊了「新百倫」商標的男子勝訴，New Balance即新百倫公司反而要賠償1,600萬美元。 （解釋到外資點解要走）<br />\n<br />\n仲記得有一單係有個女仔被官二代之類強姦，最後不了了之。有冇人可以補充。<br />\n<br />\n希望整完個list 出嚟後可以 share 俾啲人睇，令佢哋知道平民百姓唔搞政治都會受影響。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cusp.hk/?p=1030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcusp.hk%2F%3Fp%3D1030&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWQy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=985f0e03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cusp.hk/?p=1030</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/113949/new-balance%E4%BE%B5%E6%AC%8A%E6%A1%88%E5%8B%9D%E8%A8%B4-3%E9%96%93new-boom%E5%BB%A0%E5%95%86%E8%A6%81%E8%B3%A01170%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F113949%2Fnew-balance%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%258B%259D%25E8%25A8%25B4-3%25E9%2596%2593new-boom%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25B3%25A01170%25E8%2590%25AC&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWQy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=2d350b4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/113949/new-balance%E4%BE%B5%E6%AC%8A%E6%A1%88%E5%8B%9D%E8%A8%B4-3%E9%96%93new-boom%E5%BB%A0%E5%95%86%E8%A6%81%E8%B3%A01170%E8%90%AC</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%B0%B7%E9%96%8B%E4%BE%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BE%2586&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWQy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=0411535f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%B0%B7%E9%96%8B%E4%BE%86</a>"},{"pid":"a596dd53730dad419033cba88453931429347ed2","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:33:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9ecea41f64284adedc6f5608e3c5484c8b738604","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:33:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4e2866deac774fb82d2bfd57eb8fd5f7175cf393","tid":1218680,"uid":26106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:34:13.000Z","msg":"孫小果案"},{"pid":"686821cd4d34a992dc31c12555e20ad436df801f","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e2866deac774fb82d2bfd57eb8fd5f7175cf393","tid":1218680,"uid":26106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:34:13.000Z","msg":"孫小果案"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"yes, thx"},{"pid":"2a27e2b567bfed1195a98b856fd46a1ecb88ee7f","tid":1218680,"uid":56636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"可以揾埋香港有邊啲法案話：過左再調整 最尾乜鳩都冇做"},{"pid":"3ddf4029ea4a1e1733df59bad98a6ad2c1b036d8","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:40:12.000Z","msg":"谷開來案： 只有政府指定律師，審訊唔公開，案件詳細資料無公開<br />\n<br />\n豆腐渣工程：黃琦撰文揭發學校的豆腐渣工程，並協助死難者的父母提出申訴，其家人在6月14日接到通知「涉嫌非法持有國家機密」將其拘留。<br />\n<br />\n楊佳案：因騎一輛無牌照自行車，受到民警的詢問和盤查，後來獲釋。然而和許多同類情況一樣，楊遭毆打至生殖器損毁。楊多次上訪均未獲合理賠償，後來更不獲理睬<br />\n<br />\n瓮安事件：少女李樹芬於瓮安縣墜河身亡。李樹芬死亡原因有可疑之處，但當局不作立案，並強行要求將屍體埋葬，李樹芬家人作出阻止遭到毆打。<br />\n<br />\n新百倫：中國法院裁決一名註冊了「新百倫」商標的男子勝訴，New Balance即新百倫公司反而要賠償1,600萬美元。 （解釋到外資點解要走）<br />\n<br />\n孫小果案： 從死刑減到有期徒刑12年，再變身夜場老闆，「假立功真減刑」逃脱專項檢查"},{"pid":"b48364d3066e84709a338dc93a9c4741f2771c80","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:41:28.000Z","msg":"最好可以有巴絲打整做傳單, poster 等啲師奶阿伯都識睇"},{"pid":"498614a5725006af2e6ac7e7eae42988b67525f3","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1ec0c4f71f1f968970dabb7ba47f69284cc140fd","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:45:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a8b0ae4ccecc8f3778803624974f2acab9a1fbcf","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:46:37.000Z","msg":"push 到上熱門"},{"pid":"e5abf3ca5ad799bd6bc2fdbc548f73894ea7e781","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"和理非嘅可以去派傳單，勇武嘅可以繼續勇武"},{"pid":"07ca152b081920adda9f318af13fa0a2e6a41478","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:51:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ad8980b2e5c4ec6ffab8310b07b7fdfe164c0acf","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2897ac516e4e7b6cbf7ca2c9191aaafc147beb27","tid":1218680,"uid":48516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:51:53.000Z","msg":"認真野太悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529f35b626c35d7a476378b07920c45e049b2f01","tid":1218680,"uid":4701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"有線中國組FB大把片,可以去睇下"}]}